Things you should know: Credit criteria fees charges and exclusions apply. Terms and conditions available on request. Offer is available on new home loan applications for refinance
purposes where foreign income is not required for serviceability and taken as part of the Advantage Package. Offer available for a limited time Residential lending is not available for Non-
Australian Resident borrowers Offer may be withdrawn at any time. Excludes refinances from Westpac St George, Bank of Melbourne, BankSA & RAMSand refinances into Owner-Occupied
Interest Only loans and Portfolio Loans. Only one cashback paid per main applicant Multiple applications submitted by the same main applicant are not eligible. Not available in conjunction

must be direct debited from this transaction account. The account must be kept open for at least 60 days after settlement and the cashback will be paid into this account during this period.
